channel.title: Run.bat NRS3Server V2 help!
channel.description:
Hey guys, I got a little problem idk how to solve! :(
Here's what happens when i Run the source: [code][Launcher] Initing Cache... Exception in thread "main" java.lang.ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException: 19 at com.rs.utils.Utils.getItemDefinitionsSize(Utils.java:268) at com.rs.cache.loaders.ItemsEquipIds.init(ItemsEquipIds.java:13) at com.rs.Launcher.main(Launcher.java:64) Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
Any suggestions?

missing the cache add your cache which ever it is 725 most preferable or do opcodes and add a 730+

either way your missing the cache add cache to data>cache
